 "instance_variables": [], "inner_classes": [], "documentation": ["Much like the property builtin, but only implements \\_\\_get\\_\\_,\nmaking it a non-data property, and can be subsequently reset.\n\nSee <http://users.rcn.com/python/download/Descriptor.htm> for more\ninformation.\n\n```pycon\n>>> class X(object):\n...   @NonDataProperty\n...   def foo(self):\n...     return 3\n>>> x = X()\n>>> x.foo\n3\n>>> x.foo = 4\n>>> x.foo\n4\n```\n\n'...' below should be 'jaraco.classes' but for pytest-dev/pytest#3396\n\\>>> X.foo\n\\<....properties.NonDataProperty object at ...>\n"]}, {"name": "jaraco.classes.properties.classproperty", "bases": [], "methods": [{"name": "jaraco.classes.properties.classproperty.__init__", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "fget", "type": {"name": "_GetterCallable[_T] | _GetterClassMethod[_T]", "xref": null, "params": null}, "default": null}, {"name": "fset", "type": {"name": "_SetterCallable[_T] | _SetterClassMethod[_T] | None", "xref": null, "params": null}, "default": "..."}], "returns": {"name": "None", "xref": {"fqname": "constants.None", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "documentation": []}, {"name": "jaraco.classes.properties.classproperty.__get__", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "instance", "type": {"name": "object", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.object", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "default": null}, {"name": "owner", "type": {"name": "type[object] | None", "xref": null, "params": null}, "default": "..."}], "returns": {"name": "_T", "xref": {"fqname": "_T", "project": null}, "params": null}, "documentation": []}, {"name": "jaraco.classes.properties.classproperty.__set__", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "owner", "type": {"name": "object", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.object", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "default": null}, {"name"